{
    "version": 4,
    "bundle": "CCQ372OZVSQHKZ4UVADWVLINHPDBMUJE",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "801032002",
    "title": "要検証・他者の介在による偶発性",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ある日、トレーニングコースで――",
            "enText": "One day, on a training course—",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "pathId": 4176166690993384175,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "今日のトレーニングプランは……。\nふむ、天候は曇り、か。",
            "enText": "Today's training plan is available \nat … Hmm, cloudy weather.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "pathId": 7900406538299169247,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "……頃合いだな。\r\nよし、そこの君に意見を求めよう！",
            "enText": "It's about time… OK, I'll ask \nyou there for your opinion!",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "pathId": -426477779300927786,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "新たな走法の研究と、瞬時の判断。\n今日の君はどちらを重視する？",
            "enText": "Researching a new running technique or \nmaking a quick decision. Which is more \nimportant to you today?",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "走法",
                    "enText": "running style",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "判断力",
                    "enText": "Judgement",
                    "nextBlock": 6
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8937782755144913879,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "うんうん、いい答えだ！\r\nウマ娘の走行技術は、常に進歩している。",
            "enText": "Yeah, yeah, that's a good answer! \nUma Musume's driving technology \nis constantly improving.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "pathId": -6720467793764585600,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "なるほど、レースは一瞬の判断が命取り。\r\n思考の速さは確かに重要だ。",
            "enText": "Well, racing is all about split-second \ndecisions. Speed of thought is \ncertainly important.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "pathId": 9048691980039083231,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "よし、参考にしよう。この偶然、\nいかなる結果をもたらすかな？",
            "enText": "Okay, let's see. What will be the \nresult of this coincidence?",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "なぜ俺に聞いたんだ？",
                    "enText": "Why did you ask me?",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "なぜ私に聞いたの？",
                    "enText": "Why did you ask me?",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4104537761915045307,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "ハハハッ、いい質問だ！",
            "enText": "Hahaha, good question!",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "pathId": 5015692200446532166,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "偶発性、セレンディピティは\r\n研究において無視できない要素だろう？",
            "enText": "Contingency and serendipity are not \nnegligible factors in research, are they?",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "pathId": -2399104997829390463,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "だから、曇りと君、2つの偶発的な\r\n『まぎれ』を利用させてもらったのさ。",
            "enText": "That's why I took advantage of two \naccidental 'blips': cloudiness and you.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "pathId": -8323012694727485867,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "君も、偶発性を大事にしてマンネリズムを\n防ぐといい！　それは真理への道だ！",
            "enText": "You, too, should value contingency and avoid \nmannerism! It's the way to the truth!",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "pathId": 1274496925478158887,
            "blockIdx": 11
        }
    ]
}